title: Sudan army chief open to negotiations - but says his troops will 'definitely' defeat paramilitary group

description: The former home of a German cannibal has been destroyed in a fire, police say.

title: Treason trial of Putin critic shows near-total removal of basic rights in Russia

description: Five of the world's largest economies are hoping to undermine Russia's grip on nuclear power supplies by shutting it out of a new alliance.

title: Air France and Airbus cleared of involuntary manslaughter over 2009 crash which killed 228 people
